OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778576786
OL,3,CTice declines to condemn councillor's
OL,4,C'Nigerians should fill pot holes'
OL,5,Cremark
OL,7,FReform UK has been accused of an
OL,8,F"utterly grotesque" failure to "call
OL,9,Fout clear racism" after its deputy
OL,10,Fleader declined to explicitly condemn
OL,11,Fcomments reportedly made by a council
OL,12,Fcandidate that Nigerians should be
OL,13,Fused to "fill in the pot holes".
OL,15,FGlenn Gibbins, who was elected as a
OL,16,FReform councillor in Sunderland in
OL,17,Fthis week's local elections, in 2024
OL,18,Fcomplained on social media about the
OL,19,F"amount of Nigerians in town".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]pD@`OUqD@QO]uD@IOUuD@_O]{D@
OL,26,AAOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
